*
*    Example of detailed, multiline chart
*
PIC  outline  size 6 3.5
TITLE at 3 3.23  font 2 text Northeast Investors
AREA at .5 .5  size 5 2.5
AXIS left  to 30
AXIS below from 85.5 to 88 boxes 5
*
*      Plot the data
*
LINE file  NEINVEST.DAT items 1 3 item 1 yymmdd
LINE file  NEINVEST.DAT items 1 2 item 1 yymmdd dotted
*
*    Add buy/sell date lines
*
ISO sparse at 851022 ver form yymmdd
LABEL      at 851022,25 xform yymmdd text BUY
ISO sparse at 860825 ver form yymmdd
LABEL      at 860825,25 xform yymmdd text SELL
*
*    Add a reference line at 13.0
*
ISO  sparse at 13
LABEL left at 85.6,13 text 13
*
*   Create a Legend with ISOs and LABELs
*
AREA at 5,.5  size .5 by .5
AXIS below to 0.5 invisible
AXIS left  to 0.5 invisible
ISO dotted  at .405
ISO  solid  at .155
LABEL right at -.05 .375  text GROWTH
LABEL right at -.05 .125  text TRUST
